          "text": "<p>How do you generate strong association rules? From the following dataset find the frequent item set using FP growth algorithm using 3 as minimum support.</p>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\" style=\"overflow-x:auto;\"><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Transaction ID</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Items</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">T1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">{K, E, M, O, Y}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">T2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">{K, E, O, Y}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">T3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">{K, E, M}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">T4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">{K, M, Y}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">T5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">{K, E, O}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>",
