          "id": "1100000448844",
          "text": "<p class=\"p1\">Given the following data set, find the frequent itemset using Apriori algorithm with minimum</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">support 3. (5)</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">T1 {A, B, C, D, E, F}</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">T2 {B, C, D, E, F, G}</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">T3 {A, D, E, H}</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">T4 {A, D, F, I, J}</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">T5 {B, D, E, K}</p>",
